    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@chrisvidal There's no current implementation of what you really want. If you want to go further on creating a specific widget, I would advise you to:\n- build a graphical mockup of the widget (how would it look in a simple way)\n- list the features available for the user\n- design a JavaScript API listing the widget options\n\nThen once you have all this design setup we can walk you through internal implementation.\n\nYou can do so in a new issue, it will be easier.\n\nThanks a lot!\n",
    "created_at": "2016-02-22T09:44:30Z",
