    "body": "@chrisvidal\n- \"algoliasearch\" is the JS API client (just handling requests to the API).\n- The helper (algoliasearch-helper) is the search state holder (what are the current refinements/query). It wraps the algoliasearch client\n- instantsearch is then wrapping helper\n\nIf you have a test repository I can have a look and help you out.\n",
